{
  "stem": "12402.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the same time, I remember what he did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Same time, he took me down to-- to the cellar, you know, and said, should anything happen, you know, to us-- he-- he knew already there's going to be problem.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Said, if anything happened, he took all his possessions, you know, like we had a lot of foreign currency, mostly-- mostly US dollars, you know, that everybody was buying for security.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father, he-- he always bought [INAUDIBLE] from the-- from the people that return from US, they always have US-- US currency-- he bought, and he took like a sugar bowl, porcelain I remember, a sugar bowl.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He put everything in that sugar bowl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were diamonds and-- and gold rings and it was-- and money, you know, a lot of-- I don't remember how many thousands of dollars.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, he put it in there and wrapped it in plastic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a very smart man, my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very well-liked in the community.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he took us down to the cellar in the corner and he made a little hole and covered it up with a-- with a rock, you know?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Covered it up, nobody would know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, remember, this is the spot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Should anything happen to us, this is gonna-- this is gonna make you survive, you know, make you survive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Money will get you anywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But don't forget where it-- Well, it was in my mind, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he hid all the shoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He showed me where we-- it was hidden, you know, under the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- Wherever he found a place, they were hidden.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and that was the beginning of the-- it was 1940.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we still went to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
